00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:04.570
The recorder typically makes use of a form for recording issues. The for

00:00:04.570 --> 00:00:08.570
includes for each issue raised, it's location within the artifact, it's

00:00:08.570 --> 00:00:13.320
description, it's type and it's severity. Issue types are artifact dependent for

00:00:13.320 --> 00:00:16.510
code review for example there may be logic issues, library issues,

00:00:16.510 --> 00:00:19.940
standards conformance issues and so on. Severity levels are also

00:00:19.940 --> 00:00:24.080
typically pre-defined, and some suggested ones are listed on the next slide.

